  <sect3 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Gnome Mahjongg</title>

    <para>
      <application>gnome-mahjongg</application> is a solitaire (one player) 
      version of the classic Eastern tile game, 
      Mahjongg. The objective is to select pairs of similar tiles. 
    </para>

    &lfs76_checked;

